The '''Municipality of Messatida''' or '''Messatis''' is an administrative district in [[Greece]]. It includes the communities of [[Krini (Achaia), Greece|Kríni]], southern [[Demenika]], [[Savalia]], and parts of [[Thea]] and [[Kallithea]].  The population is over 10,000.  It is home to about 6% of the Patras urban population.  Its area is 80-100 km².  Forests cover about 20% to 30% of the municipality, urban houses and buildings cover about 5%, and the rest remains pasture and rocky mountains ([[Omplos]]).

