==Communities==
*[[Kallithea (Achaia), Greece|Kallithea]]
*[[Krini (Achaia), Greece|Krini]]
*[[Krystallovrysi (Achaia), Greece|Krystallovrysi]]
*[[Ovrya, Greece|Ovrya]]
*[[Petroto, Achaia|Petroto]]
*[[Saravali]]
**[[Demenika]] (southern and central part)
*[[Thea (Achaia), Greece|Thea]]
The town hall is on Demokratías Street in Ovrya not far from the centre and Thea and Kallithea.

It was one of the [[Mycenae]]an villages that formed [[Patras]]<!--Yes, in name, but is there evidence that ancient Messatis and the present-day municipality occupy the same geographical area?-->.

